      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>Wait, I'm confused. You just said I should give him 200-300mg of aspirin, but then you said I shouldn't give him aspirin because of Reye's syndrome? Which is it? I'm really worried about his fever right now and just want to know what to do.",
